{"tid":2249819,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新巴職工會10.8致函李家超促解釋：向突然橫越路面的障礙物響按是否違法","createTime":"2020-10-19T14:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T15:58:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"49ed777dfa05e546a0594b112e7a74a427131b71","tid":2249819,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"上月「9.6九龍大遊行」，新巴970路線車長駕駛期間被警方拘捕，一度指控他無故響按、快速行駛，並稱他攜「士巴拿」開工，涉藏有攻擊性武器，最終落案起訴他不小心駕駛罪。不少車長帶備「士巴拿」以便調校巴士的倒後鏡至合適角度，事件引起前線司機擔憂，害怕因而誤墮法網。<br />\n<br />\n新巴職工會早前向保安局局長李家超發公開信，要求保安局就此事向業界解說。工會主席林錦標回覆《蘋果》查詢，本月8日已向保安局寄信，惟至今仍未獲回覆，促當局回答他們的提問，澄清執法標準。至於被控車長已復工，新巴亦繼續為其提供法律支援。保安局回覆本報查詢時確認已收到相關信件，指會於稍後回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/KTDYN7TL55FXTBNSKRK5ORN35Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FKTDYN7TL55FXTBNSKRK5ORN35Q%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZsljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=9025788a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FKTDYN7TL55FXTBNSKRK5ORN35Q%2F&h=b7d21ae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/KTDYN7TL55FXTBNSKRK5ORN35Q/</a>"},{"pid":"22a27f94234d55c68eb245681140d6a91c1df696","tid":2249819,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b58939e75881732b87e981a6477f8912abb153f","tid":2249819,"uid":271513,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"警甴的確係障礙物"},{"pid":"3d836e0dd97980c375450a1824b4532daa62f8b0","tid":2249819,"uid":168389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T15:13:53.000Z","msg":"癲狗話再嘈拉埋你<i